{"304030":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"ArcheAge","steam_appid":304030,"required_age":"17","is_free":true,"dlc":[553920],"detailed_description":"<h1>Revelation is Live!<\/h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ArcheAge 3.0: Revelation is here! <\/h2>Play as the stout Dwarves and fearsome Warborn, unleash game changing Abyssal Power skills, explore beautiful new zones, settle in new residential areas, and more!<br><img src=\"http:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/304030\/extras\/Revelation_slide.jpg?t=1487716103\"><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ArcheAge is the ultimate free-to-play fantasy-sandbox MMORPG<\/h2>Build massive castles and lay claim to lands whose riches fuel a deep, player-driven economy. Band together to protect your fortune in epic siege battles and naval combat \u2013 or live the life of an outlaw, prying glory and coin from foes left in your wake.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shape the World<\/h2>Gatherers, crafters, and traders are the engine that drives ArcheAge, and its economy is yours to control. Master diverse skills to craft trade goods, houses, ships and castles. Transport and trade materials across the realm, braving danger and piracy to support your allies in wars that will change the fate of the world. Join a zone\u2019s community and work together to unlock special regional bonuses or form a family with your closest friends.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight for Glory<\/h2>Assemble allies and build an empire to span continents. Sabotage your enemies\u2019 trade and lay waste to their armies in the field. Rally your forces and craft massive siege engines to storm the heart of rival castles and claim them as your own, or test your skill against hundreds of other players in open world battlegrounds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Set Sail<\/h2>Sail the vast uncharted ocean and amass fame and fortune by securing trade routes and controlling the flow of enemies\u2019 resources. Riches await, whether you lead fleets against rival armadas or ply the waters as a pirate for hire \u2013 just beware what lies beneath!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rule a Nation<\/h2>Conquer and improve one of the six Auroran Castles to prove the might of your guild and create your own nation! Develop your nation\u2019s resources and convince other guilds to join you. Choose the faction you want to align with by convincing their heroes to ally with you. Expand your territory by conquering the other Auroran Castles and fend off sieges from those seeking to claim your nation as their own!","about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ArcheAge is the ultimate free-to-play fantasy-sandbox MMORPG<\/h2>Build massive castles and lay claim to lands whose riches fuel a deep, player-driven economy. Band together to protect your fortune in epic siege battles and naval combat \u2013 or live the life of an outlaw, prying glory and coin from foes left in your wake.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shape the World<\/h2>Gatherers, crafters, and traders are the engine that drives ArcheAge, and its economy is yours to control. Master diverse skills to craft trade goods, houses, ships and castles. Transport and trade materials across the realm, braving danger and piracy to support your allies in wars that will change the fate of the world. Join a zone\u2019s community and work together to unlock special regional bonuses or form a family with your closest friends.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight for Glory<\/h2>Assemble allies and build an empire to span continents. Sabotage your enemies\u2019 trade and lay waste to their armies in the field. Rally your forces and craft massive siege engines to storm the heart of rival castles and claim them as your own, or test your skill against hundreds of other players in open world battlegrounds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Set Sail<\/h2>Sail the vast uncharted ocean and amass fame and fortune by securing trade routes and controlling the flow of enemies\u2019 resources. Riches await, whether you lead fleets against rival armadas or ply the waters as a pirate for hire \u2013 just beware what lies beneath!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rule a Nation<\/h2>Conquer and improve one of the six Auroran Castles to prove the might of your guild and create your own nation! Develop your nation\u2019s resources and convince other guilds to join you. Choose the faction you want to align with by convincing their heroes to ally with you. Expand your territory by conquering the other Auroran Castles and fend off sieges from those seeking to claim your nation as their own!","short_description":"Revelation is here! Journey into the storied fantasy world of ArcheAge, the ultimate sandbox MMO built on player choice and empowerment.","supported_languages":"English<strong>*<\/strong>, French<strong>*<\/strong>, German<strong>*<\/strong><br><strong>*<\/strong>languages with full audio support","reviews":"\u201cWith ArcheAge, the freedom of how to play is what sets it apart from other online games both free to play and subscription based.\u201d<br>8.8\/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=http:\/\/www.gamingnexus.com\/Article\/4546\/ArcheAge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gaming Nexus<\/a><br><br>\u201cClosest thing to a true fantasy sandbox experience on the market\u201d<br>8\/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=http:\/\/www.pcgamesn.com\/archeage\/archeage-review-progress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >PCGamesN<\/a><br><br>\u201cSheer depth of the PVP and tradeskill system make it into the EVE-Online of the fantasy genre\u201d<br>85\/100 \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=http:\/\/gamingtrend.com\/reviews\/archeage-enticing-youd-probably-willing-stand-line\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gaming Trend<\/a><br>","header_image":"https:\/\/steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net\/steam\/apps\/304030\/header.jpg?t=1487716103","website":"http:\/\/www.trionworlds.com\/archeage\/en\/?affiliateId=251","pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum: